      t.isLE_shift _ a n b (by rw [add_comm, h])
    exact t.isLE_of_iso ((shiftFunctor A i).mapIso (((Gr_commShift L).iso i n (i - n)
      (by simp)).app X) ‚â™‚â´ (shiftFunctorAdd' A (i - n) n i (by simp)).app _).symm b

